race.description: Sportsbet Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: ACT NATURAL (1) continues to knock on the door, placing in all 11 starts, and gets another terrific opportunity to finally shed the maiden tag. Only needs to hold his current level to be right in the finish again. BRIMARVI ROSEMARIE (6) is in a similar boat, honest without breaking through. Again left herself with too much to do last start before hitting the line strongly. If she can settle a touch closer, she'll take plenty of stopping. PRETTY MORSEL (9) has built nicely through the campaign and should be nearing her peak now fourth-up. Needs a touch of luck from the wide draw but can feature. HOMETOWN GAL (7) improved sharply last start when sent forward on the main track, only to be claimed late. Strips fitter and is in the mix. ILLUSTRATES (8) was below her best last time but her run two back was solid. From the favourable draw, she's worth keeping safe in exotics.
